==Dutch==

===Personal pronoun===
[[Category:Dutch personal pronouns]]
'''gij''' (''mute form'' '''[[ge]]''')
# ''Second-person singular:'' [[thou]] (''dialectal'').

====Usage notes====
The personal pronoun ''[[gij]]'' and its variants are now restricted to religious context, and are considered archaic in the Netherlands. In Flanders, ''[[gij]]'' is still commonly used as the second-person singular. The best translation in both cases would be ''[[thou]]''.